      "value": "<p>Keywords: Bukijutsu</p><p>You generate a surge of chakra throughout your body preparing for a powerful burst of speed and power. You gain 3 additional actions as a part of the activation of this jutsu until the end of your turn, which you then gain 5 exhaustion. These actions must be used to perform multiple bukijutsu in a row. </p>",
